dct_description_sm: Includes index of banks, government buildings, hotels, sports complexes, entertainment centers, hospitals, stations, public service centers, restaurants, and sites of interest. Recto: location map of Panama showing roads and territories; inset map of Panama City showing sports complexes with index of places of interest; inset map of Colón showing roads, banks, public buildings, hotels, entertainment centers, and stations. Verso: text; inset showing location of a sports complex; inset map showing Panama Viejo, Villa Maria, and sports complexes with Catedral de Panama Viejo represented pictorially.
